title: Fort Dupont Park: Multimedia Presentations
body: Explore This Park    Learn About the Park     Photos & Multimedia     Multimedia Presentations              Multimedia Presentations                         Fort Dupont Park Summer Concert Series 40th Anniversary Fort Dupont Park Summer Concert Series celebrated its 40th Anniversary in 2012. From Rose Royce to ZAPP and of course Roy Ayers Fort Dupont Park has a rich tradition of showcasing top notch performers with up and coming new talent. The shows are free and open to anyone and everyone.
